LibreRouterOS Build Environment
==============================

This build environment contains containerized build tools and automation
scripts for LibreRouterOS, which is based on OpenWrt and LibreMesh.

The build system solves common OpenWrt build issues including:
- GLIBC version compatibility
- Python 2.x requirements  
- Missing upstream scripts
- Build environment isolation

Components:
- Docker containerization (Ubuntu 18.04 + Python 2.7)
- Build automation and orchestration
- OpenWrt script collection and integration
- Real-time monitoring and validation
- Comprehensive documentation

This software is distributed under the GNU General Public License v3 or later,
maintaining compatibility with the OpenWrt and LibreMesh ecosystems.